Text:
When I extract KMSnano.exe to a folder I find the KMSELDI executable.
I edit the "Manual_Silent.com" txt fille with the parameters "/noWin /no2013"
 I open a CMD with admin privileges and launch KMSELDI. 
A window pops up with the title of "KMS GUI ELDI" and it asks for the KMS HOST IP or Name and it has the value of "1688_" as the port already.
What would I put in for the IP or the name?
If I don't enter anything it won't work, if I try to enter in my default gateway IP or the computer's IP it just retries over and over again.
I ended up just launching KMSnano but I hope it didn't screw up my windows 7 64-bit.
